Annexure A — Background Verification and Personal Data Consent
I, [Candidate Name], hereby expressly consent to Omninuera and its authorized background-verification service providers collecting, storing and processing my personal data for the purpose of pre-employment background verification, including identity verification, education and employment history checks, references, and any other checks required for the recruitment and compliance process. I confirm that:
- The Company is the data fiduciary for this processing and I may contact the Company’s Data Protection Officer at [DPO name and email] for privacy queries.
- The categories of personal data to be processed include identity and contact information, educational records, employment history, references, and any other information necessary for verification.
- The purpose of processing is limited to pre-employment background verification and related compliance.
- My personal data may be shared with and processed by third-party verification service providers, which may be located outside India. I consent to such cross-border transfers provided the Company implements appropriate safeguards.
- The Company will retain verification data only as necessary for recruitment and legal compliance and in accordance with its privacy notice [insert privacy notice URL].
- I understand that I may withdraw consent in writing to the Company, subject to legal or contractual restrictions and the Company’s need to retain certain data for compliance; withdrawal will not affect processing already lawfully completed.
Signature: ________________________  Date: ________

Notes
- This document is an HR draft prepared for Legal review. It is not a final, legally reviewed offer. Please forward to Legal for review and approval prior to issuing to the candidate.
